Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:09.32,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Yoshikage... My son...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:12.49,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:16.45,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've hidden yourself \Nand changed your face and name by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:20.79,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,How unfortunate... And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:25.63,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Right. We need to look into everyone who's gone missing recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.42,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Including runaways.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.80,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kira is probably still in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:34.63,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Do you think he would attempt to \Ncommit murder while in hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:40.01,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It's not easy for serial killers like him to control their impulses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:41.98,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He'll strike again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:49.11,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Do we really not have to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:52.78,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,We still don't have any clue where Kira could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:54.90,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.78,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Mr. Jotaro said it was fine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:03.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,He said we should keep going to school \Nlike normal students until he has more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.83,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Be better t'keep looking for Kira than wastin' time studyin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:12.51,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,It'll be a piece of cake this time \Nsince we already got him cornered once, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:19.10,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Yes. As long as I'm repairing my house, \NI'd like to have some renovations done, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:23.77,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Damn him! He's taken pictures of all those businessmen in an attempt to find my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:26.39,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Could you send someone over to give me an estimate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:30.44,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Jotaro and all those other Stand users \Nare doing as they please...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:36.95,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,I need to make more Stand users \Nto deal with these meddlesome troublemakers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.33,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:48.71,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:52.59,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Even though his appearance has changed, \Nour father-son bond has drawn us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.96,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,I know my son when I see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.97,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,I've finally found you, Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.89,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I need to figure out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:06.85,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,...who this guy disguised as my Papa really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.35,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:14.36,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,At this rate, those damned Stand users will...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.61,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,I won't allow it! \NI won't allow that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.99,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,I swear I will protect Yoshikage!
