Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:55.33,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,513)\pos(141,887)\fs60}Episode 31: {\fs80} July 15th (Thursday) Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.66,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.83,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm gonna be late! And I have class duties today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Man, I was up way too late last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:10.89,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I feel fuckin' fantastic after all the sleep I got last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.52,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Look at that, Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.48,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Those're binoculars!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.02,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,They're just sittin' there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.82,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You really can't help but \Nget distracted by things on the ground, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,They're probably super dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.24,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.49,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I most certainly am {\i1}not {\i0}dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.87,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Hello Josuke and Okuyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.16,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Th-That was you? \NMikitaka, you can't just scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:36.33,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Nearly gave me a fuckin' heart attack, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.92,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Oh, that's quite enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Quit acting bashful.\N It wasn't a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:43.05,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,But hey, good timin'! \NI wanted t'ask ya somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:46.64,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I wantcha t'be totally straight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.39,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,That alien stuff is all bullshit, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:53.48,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You're just a Stand user who thinks \Nhe's an alien or somethin', ain'tcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.60,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Just fuckin' say if ya are or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.69,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I have been truthful with you from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.32,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I am a space alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.99,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Why're ya suddenly talkin' like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.45,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,C'mon, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:08.78,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Anyway, why were you sitting there in the middle\N of the road transformed into a pair of binoculars?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:13.41,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I was waiting here so that I could show you both that structure in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.96,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,That thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.67,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,That structure is a transmission tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.67,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Transmission tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:24.42,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, it doesn't do anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.97,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,They put it out of commission and disconnected all the cables.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:33.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Once Morioh began developing residential areas, they retired the transmission tower and started putting all the cables underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.56,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,So what's the deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You trying to establish contact \Nwith another planet or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:43.07,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,There is smoke coming from its center, is there not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.53,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.36,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Y-You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.20,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Please use me to take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.46,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Wh-Whoa, hey! It's a kettle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.01,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,What?! What's that doin' up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.26,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,It's twenty meters off the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.97,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Would you please look about five meters higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.56,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What is all that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.89,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I-I wanna see, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.61,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! Un-fuckin'-believable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.16,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,There's a guy up there! \NHe's cookin' somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.41,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He must be livin' on the transmission tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.08,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He's got all the stuff he needs there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.00,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He's up there catchin' fish an' growin' cucumbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.84,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He's got it made!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:48.38,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That's amazing! \NHe's completely self-sufficient up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:52.35,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,The people of your planet seem to relish in odd behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.06,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.94,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,H-He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.24,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,He's a new Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.70,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Yeah! He started flyin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:17.41,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But what is a Stand user doing living up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:22.04,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I suppose it is in your best interest \Nto learn more of this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.17,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I finally see them. About time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.97,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Have they taken an interest in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.97,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:35.47,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I last spoke to another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:39.98,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Look... He saw us now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.56,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Wanna check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:48.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We can't be sure if this new Stand user\N is an enemy or a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.33,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? C-Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.58,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm in a bit of a hurry right... now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.58,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.97,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Gettin' close to this thing, it's a lot bigger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.89,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You two, stop right there! {Mikitaka isn't in human form during this shot keep in mind, so he only sees Josuke and Okuyasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.22,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer to this transmission tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:19.97,Main,Dudes,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.23,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You need to step further away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:26.81,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I just finished using the toilet, \Nso you better step back if you know what's best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.20,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Don't fuckin' tell me this's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.95,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Can't say I didn't warn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.78,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Not my fault you got covered in my feces and urine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.78,Secondary,Josuke,0,0,0,,Th-That's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.08,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Disgusting? How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:46.50,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I set it up to spray like that so I could fertilize the wildflowers down below!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.46,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I like to recycle as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.67,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,To your right I have Asiatic dayflowers, \Nmountain udo, and watercress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.22,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,They're all edible wildflowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:02.98,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,And best of all, with all these wildflowers around, \NI can catch and eat any rabbits who try to eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:06.31,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Do you actually live up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:10.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Doesn't this transmission tower \Nbelong to the electric company?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.57,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.07,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I bought this place with my own hard-earned money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:21.29,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I got this abandoned transmission tower for just one-hundred \Nthousand yen and turned it into my own self-sufficient dwelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.54,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ya bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.95,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,For one-hundred thousand yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.67,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Yup! Just one-hundred thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:30.13,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Since I'm self-sufficient, \NI don't have to work anywhere anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:36.05,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,And even if I never left, I get all the exercise I need just by moving around the transmission tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.68,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Get a load of the amazing view I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.85,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Huh? H-Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:45.60,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Even if you never left? \NJust how long have you been staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.52,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Let's see... About three years now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.10,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Th{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.44,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Three years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.78,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I don't think I've touched the ground for at least a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:10:00.24,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Yo, Josuke... \NI ain't never knew a guy this fuckin' stupid lived here in Morioh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:04.29,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He's a fuckin' nutcase!\N An' he sure as shit ain't our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:07.12,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ain't no way he's gonna attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.25,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:12.92,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,For now, I guess we should \Nhead back and report this to Mr. Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.26,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.97,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Something about this seems off to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.94,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,What was this boy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:34.23,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,I see no issue with him recording video footage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:39.15,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,The way he's hiding behind that pillar suggests he's gathering evidence like I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:43.70,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,He must be following someone\N and recording their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.91,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Could he be recording one of these men?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.88,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Kawajiri Hayato, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.67,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,There's something very strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.59,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,...about this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.40,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.02,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.44,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Josuke, did you leave for school yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.19,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.87,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:32.92,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Josuke, you little shit! I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:38.63,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,The nerve of him to take a bite out of my Kamakura Custar,\N then put it back in the fridge half-eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:43.18,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Not to mention there should still be two in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.89,Main,Tomoko,0,0,0,,Sometimes he really pisses me off...{This line is also in episode 32}{Updated for blu-rays}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:57.27,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy! Something just fell out of your pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.74,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Is that a photo or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.45,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Can you two please leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.41,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Don't feel like you have to pick it up! I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:09.29,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Looks like a polaroid photo. What's he panicking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.75,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Seriously, it's fine! Just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.67,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.88,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Hey! J-J-Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.47,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That's... Kira's dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.97,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I knew his dad's ghost was involved with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:28.97,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You finally stepped inside! I've been waiting for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:34.35,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You never would have stepped inside \Nif I had asked you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.23,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,But by telling you not to come in, \Nyou got angry and came in anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:41.40,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You've finally stepped into Superfly, Higashikata Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.16,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Well done, Kanedaichi Toyohiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.83,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,You've done well to lure that idiotic Josuke into your Superfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.87,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.75,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Somethin' ain't right! Get back here, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:59.04,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can't! Kira's dad is right here! \NHe has the arrow with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.38,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:16.19,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Once someone has entered the transmission tower, \Nthey can't leave until another person comes in and takes their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:20.77,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,If you try to force your way out, \Nyou become part of the transmission tower itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:24.90,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,That's the power of my Stand, Superfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.32,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,You completely fell for it, Higashikata Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:33.04,Main,Yoshihiro,0,0,0,,Make sure he never escapes, Kanedaichi Toyohiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.42,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Comment: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.34,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.47,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Sh-Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:58.23,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Even though it's my Stand,\N I have no direct control over Superfly itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.69,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You could call it an independent Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.53,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I can finally leave now that you showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:07.99,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Even I, its user, was held captive by my Superfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.49,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Well, good luck living here in my stead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.45,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,That motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.33,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He musta been workin' with \Nthat old geezer from the photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:21.25,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Okuyasu, can I be of assistance in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.59,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You'd just get hurt, so stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.88,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You've done enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:32.47,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Maybe if ya could turn into dynamite instead of just dice or binoculars or whatever, then maybe ya could help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.68,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:40.40,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,I cannot exert strength beyond my own, and I certainly \Ncannot transform into something as complex as dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.31,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,But I believe I could be of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.57,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:46.44,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I just finished tellin' ya there ain't nothin' you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.66,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Leave the dangerous shit t'us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:54.37,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,That fucker's tryin' t'get away since he thinks he's got him trapped in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.37,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,...but he ain't never met the likes of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.37,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey... You thinking what I'm thinking, Okuyasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.84,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You bet I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.42,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ain't nothin' special about a stupid ol' transmission tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.38,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Let's fuck it up, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:12.39,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll have no problem getting out after we destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:14.60,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorarara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.15,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.65,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,What the hell? How are they so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.57,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,This thing's pretty tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:31.41,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,So long as we keep at it, we'll snap the thing in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:35.03,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,An' look up there! He's about t'fall off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.54,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Y-You idiots! How could you commit such a heinous act?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:41.21,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I knew this was a possibility, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.79,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:49.17,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,The transmission tower absorbed the power from your attacks and is redistributing the force throughout the entire structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.05,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Huh? What the fuck's this retard talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:55.35,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke, just a little more an' you'll be outta there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.51,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hold on, Okuyasu! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.44,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Something isn't right... What's that weird noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:15.49,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,It's the force from your attacks \Nmoving inside the transmission tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.33,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.49,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Consider this fact for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:21.54,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You know all about the conservation of energy and all that, right? {-twitch twitch- -Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:26.17,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,That stored power has to escape from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.34,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Where do you think it's all gonna end up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.96,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Duck, Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:50.90,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You can attack it all you like, but any damage you do \Nto the transmission tower will come straight back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:54.20,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Hit it and get hit back. Cut it and get cut back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.99,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Consider the implications here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:59.91,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,No matter what ability anyone who \Ntries to help you happens to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.91,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,...they can't ever destroy the transmission tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.42,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.79,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Th-This ain't good, Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.63,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,The thing hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.92,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I got a hole in my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.39,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I suppose I should have warned you beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:22.56,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Now I bet you're thinking that if you defeat me, \Nthe user, you'll be able to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.60,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,But that won't work, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.73,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Like I said earlier,\N this transmission tower is an independent Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:33.82,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Even if I died, this transmission tower would probably \Nkeep trapping people inside of it for all of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.07,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,That's the power of Superfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:38.87,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.08,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,All of eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.08,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,But don't feel too down about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:49.33,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You just need to lure someone else inside, Higashikata Josuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.30,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,One comes in, one comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:56.55,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Just lure a sucker into taking your place and make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:59.72,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,It's just like the card game Old Maid. {fyi, the goal in Old Maid is to pass off any queens you have since the person left with the last queen, the old maid, loses}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.81,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Society works pretty much the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.85,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,All you have to do is pass the old maid off to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.94,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:11.73,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,You are correct in stating that if Josuke were to lure someone else inside, he could get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.23,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:14.99,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.78,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,But you will be the one to take his place \Ninside the transmission tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.33,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,In you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.08,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.83,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Mikitaka! When did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.54,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.08,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Why were you an electric cable? \NWhen did you get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.13,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,What's up with your ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.21,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:39.18,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,For you see, I am a space alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.18,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:43.68,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Y-You really {\i1}can{\i0} be useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:47.52,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,This is your chance! \NPlease step outside, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.89,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.27,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I really gotta hand it to ya, Mikitaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.19,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke, hurry an' get outta there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.11,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Get outta the transmission tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.58,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:07.04,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You bastard! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:12.08,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,The old fart in the photo \Nnever told me Josuke had a friend like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:16.67,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,Being a space alien, I am unfamiliar with this game of Old Maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:20.68,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,However, for you to deceive Josuke \Nand tell him that he cannot leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:25.26,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,...is akin to an adult beating a small child \Nat a game they had no hope of winning, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.81,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,That is why it is you who should\N remain in the transmission tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.31,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,You will be the one to remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:42.61,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,After living here for so long, \NI developed thick calluses all over my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.45,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I can hide things underneath them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.62,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:53.92,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,You appear to be under the impression that you have \Ncut a part of my body, but that is incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.42,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,What you have cut is not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:59.88,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,...but the cable from the transmission tower \Nwhich you clung to earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.14,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:09.06,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Good job! \NNow reach the top and get out of there, Mikitaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.06,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I've waited so long for someone like you to step inside this transmission tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.44,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Did you really think I would let you escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:20.78,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I've thought of nothing else but \Ngetting out of here every single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.74,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Did you forget already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:32.62,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,The transmission tower returns any damage done to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.71,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,That cable is part of the tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:39.13,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I cut the cable at just the right angle \Nto send the force back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:42.38,Main,Mikitaka,0,0,0,,H-Have I been defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.22,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,M-Mikitaka! Hurry up and get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can heal that wound for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.93,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.31,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,I'm the only one leaving here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.90,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Perfect angle and direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:01.28,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Once struck, it strikes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.82,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Mikitaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.28,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Y-You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:12.16,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You really put me through the wringer\N trying to get out of here, but now I'm in the clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:16.25,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,It's really gonna hurt when you\N pull those things out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.00,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,...you'll have plenty of time to treat those wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:22.13,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,You can use the medicinal plants\N I've been growing down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:26.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Asshole! Do you really think you'll \Nget away with this just because you got out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.85,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'll chase you to the ends of the earth, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.39,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,Of course I'll get away! It's simple. {This line and the next are in episode 32 and updated for blu-rays}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:37.35,Main,Toyohiro,0,0,0,,It's not like you guys have found \NKira Yoshikage yet, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:53.50,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Who is this? I've never seen him before. {Line also in episode 32}{Updated for blu-rays}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:23.94,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'll expose him... no matter what.
